text: @SenRickScott Rep mark green of Tennessee is upset that Pelosi wants to investigate the federal government response to Coronavirus. We did it for 9-11. What’s wrong? Oh by the way the senate is still moving forward with investigating hunter Biden. Do they have time for that too?
